Journals publishing software papers in ecology, evolution & environment


A directory of journals publishing software papers related to ecology, evolution & environment:

Check out the Software Sustainability Institute for a more comprehensive list (all disciplines).

For Data Papers, check out GBIF directory of journals publishing biodiversity-related Data Papers.

Journals

OA (Open Access):

  • Yes: All articles are published open access, sometimes after paying an Article Processing Change (APC) fee.

  • Hybrid: Some articles are published open access, usually after paying an Article Processing Change (APC) fee.

Article Processing Charges (APC) may not be up to date. Also, many journals offer fee waivers and discounts. Please check the journal website.

Journal Rank data from Scimago. Please visit their website for more details.

Contributing

If you find an error or want to add new journals, please open an issue or a pull request on GitHub.
